title: #92Noon! Zimmer/Brackett/Leber/BirkBit
description: Hear Mike Zimmer's weekly chat with PA on X'sO's, then the Wild's director of amateur scouting Judd Brackett takes us through the 2020 NHL Draft, Leber from Chicago before he analyzes Bucs/Bears, and Matt Birk is in studio! Vikings talkers and more throughout!
